 the freedom to drive longer distances between charges.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s anticipated that Chevy will offer attractive lease incentives to help persuade those on the fence about switching from a traditional gas vehicle to an all-electric one.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"general-motors-pushes-forward-with-electrification\"\u003eGeneral Motors pushes forward with electrification\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe 2025 Chevy Equinox EV is part of General Motors’ broader plan to expand its electric vehicle lineup. GM has committed to an all-electric future, with a goal of offering 30 new EV models globally by 2025.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"2024 Chevrolet Equinox EV\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIzMDg3MzQz/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg\" height=\"3800\" width=\"5700\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e2024 Chevrolet Equinox EV\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChevy\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"chevrolet-equinox-ev-production-and-availability\"\u003eChevrolet Equinox EV production and availability\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eChevrolet has confirmed that production of the 2025 Equinox EV will take place at GM’s Ramos Arizpe plant in Mexico, which is already responsible for assembling other Chevrolet models. This facility plays a key role in GM’s production pipeline, and the automaker expects to scale production to meet anticipated demand for the new Equinox EV.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/fiat-500e-flops-is-stellantis-throwing-away-110-million\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003cp\u003eChevy plans to have the Equinox EV available in dealerships by late 2024, with pre-orders open now through the Chevrolet website. Deliveries are expected to start in early 2025.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.webp 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.webp 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.webp 700w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1240px) 700px, (min-width: 675px) 620px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_380/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg 380w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_620/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg 620w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg 700w\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"2024 Chevrolet Equinox EV\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/t_share/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_700/MjEwMTY4NDA2MDIyODkwNzM1/2024-chevrolet-equinox-ev.jpg\" height=\"3802\" width=\"5700\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" itemprop=\"contentUrl url\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"caption\"\u003e2024 Chevrolet Equinox EV\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eChevy\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe 2025 Chevy Equinox EV brings an attractive package to the electric vehicle market with its impressive 300+ mile range and affordable $35,000 price tag. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s hard to deny that Chevy has delivered a well-rounded, feature-rich EV at a price point that could tempt many buyers. However, with recent reports of EV sales slowing and consumer hesitancy around fully transitioning to electric, it will be interesting to see how the Equinox EV is received. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile it ticks a lot of boxes in terms of affordability and practicality, the real question remains: will it be enough to convince a broader audience to make the switch from traditional gas-powered vehicles?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-super-link href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/volkswagens-cutting-edge-ev-factory-spirals-toward-collapse-as-demand-crumbles\" onclick=\"return window.phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"Embed Card Click\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-super-link\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003csection id=\"phximagetilehub-3\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-hub data-group-size=\"9\" data-first-group-size=\"9\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cphoenix-non-personalized-recommendations-no-tracking config=\"{\u0026#34;siteBasePath\u0026#34;:null,\u0026#34;size\u0026#34;:3,\u0026#34;widgetName\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;tempestn_tile-hub_autoblog_article-page_title-not-found-1-1\u0026#34;}\"\u003e\u003c/phoenix-non-personalized-recommendations-no-tracking\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/phoenix-hub\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
